HEADWORD: Agavaceae
<hw>Agavaceae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fr>1</fr> <def>a natural
family of chiefly tropical and xerophytic plants: includes Dracenaceae
(Dracaenaceae); comprises plants that in some classifications are
divided between the Amaryllidaceae and the Liliaceae.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Agavaceae</fam>, agave family, sisal
family.</syn>⟦br⟧
